Package com.commander4j.db

Class JDBInterfaceRequest

java.lang.Object
com.commander4j.db.JDBInterfaceRequest
public class JDBInterfaceRequest extends Object
JDBInterfaceRequest is used by the outbound interface process by inserting a record into the SYS_INTERFACE_REQUEST table. Whenever a process needs to generate an outbound message a request record is put into the table SYS_INTERFACE_REQUEST The request record contains a reference to the transaction number within the APP_PALLET_HISTORY_TABLE.
